word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词，可指事物本质上的差异或数量上的差额，也可指事物在某一方面的差别，还可指人们之间的不同意见。
较正式用词，除指事物在本质上的差别外，还指在某一方面或某一细节上的区分，要在认真观察、研究后才易觉察。
侧重指在判断、见识方面的差别，也可指待遇上的区别。
多用于言论和记述方面，指两物之间缺乏使之相似或平衡的协调。

list.abstract: difference（[ˈdɪfrəns]），英语单词。作名词为差异点；不同之处；差异。作动词为附加图记于。例句：Difference between older and younger Chinese buyers.（中国老年和年轻买家的区别。） 作名词时，近义词为diversity、conflict、disparity。反义词为sameness。

yingyinNormal.en: What, you know what? You guys are wrong. Yes, there is a chronological age difference but I never notice it. You know why? Because she is very mature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过你们都错了，没错，我们是有年龄上的差异，但是我都感觉不到，为什么？因为她很成熟。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? I wanted to make a difference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们知道吗？我想打造不同的新面貌。

yingyinNormal.en: No! That's where I sit! What's the difference?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，这是我的专座！有区别吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Cuba. Russia. America. It makes no difference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 古巴，俄罗斯，美国，都没有区别。

yingyinNormal.en: The main difference with this dough is coarser.
yingyinNormal.zh: 与这个不同的是，现在的比较粗糙。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you're forgetting about the time difference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，你忘了把时差算进去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Really. What color is it? What difference does that make?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是喔？什么颜色？什么颜色有差别吗？

yingyinNormal.en: The difference between us is our knowledge and technology.
yingyinNormal.zh: 区别只是我们的知识和科技。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that's the difference between us. I don't believe it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就是我们俩之间的不同了，我不信这些。

yingyinNormal.en: Then what difference does it make? What difference does it make? Here we go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我坐哪有什么区别？有什么区别？好戏登场。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the difference between a soft one and a hard one?
yingyinNormal.zh: 软和硬开张有啥区别吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Now we're back live. Okay, yeah. I can see the difference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在回到现场直播了。好，我能看出跟之前的差别。

yingyinNormal.en: I would like to be a journalist. I want to make a difference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要成为一名新闻工作者，我要改变世界。

yingyinNormal.en: Which makes all the difference. It makes the loss greater, yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就了不起了。因此损失严重，没错。

yingyinNormal.en: Get me his contact info. It won't make a difference calling him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 给我他的联系电话。打给他不能改变什么的。

yingyinNormal.en: And it might make a big difference for your family's bottom line.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它可能给你的家庭财务底线带来巨大变化。

yingyinNormal.en: IT technology and digital technology, is not the technology difference, is the difference of the way people think, the way people deal with the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: IT科技和数字科技，这不仅仅是不同的技术，而是人们思考方式的不同，人们对待这个世界方式的不同。

yingyinNormal.en: Take a high-speed ride with a difference, at Atlantis Dolphin Bay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在「亚特兰蒂斯海豚湾」踏上与别不同的高速之旅。

yingyinNormal.en: Your facts or mine? What's the difference? Mine are the true facts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的事实还是我的？有什么区别？我的事实才是事实。

yingyinNormal.en: Well what's the difference? Your eggs aren't here anymore, are they?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那有什么差别呢？你的蛋已经不在这个地方了。

examination_example.sentence: There is a <highlight>difference</highlight> between arguing and fighting.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 争吵和打架是有区别的。

examination_example.sentence: He began studying them, trying to learn the <highlight>differences</highlight> between the birds and noticing their different behaviors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他开始研究它们，试图了解鸟类之间的差异，并注意到它们不同的行为。

examination_example.sentence: "Just five more minutes outdoors can make a <highlight>difference</highlight>," David Bond says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大卫·邦德说：“只要在户外多呆5分钟就能有所改变。”

examination_example.sentence: But does one plastic straw or cup really make a <highlight>difference</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但一根塑料吸管或杯子真的能带来改变吗？

examination_example.sentence: In the beginning, I dared myself to make a <highlight>difference</highlight> in the life of another person.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一开始，我敢于让自己为另一个人的生活带来改变。

examination_example.sentence: Although there was an age <highlight>difference</highlight>, we both came from a tradition of theater and live TV.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然有年龄差异，但我们都有来自戏剧和电视直播的传统。

examination_example.sentence: Large outdoor theater with the closest seats under cover (price <highlight>difference</highlight>).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大型户外影院，最近的座位上有遮盖（价格差异）。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
